These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, juice
The people have 2 different jobs:  chef, firefighter
There are 2 different nationalities: argentine, indian
The people use 2 different means of transport: train, snowmobile
1. the firefighter is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
2. the chef is on the right of the firefighter##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage      | juice      | coffee    |
| Job           | firefighter | chef |
| Nationality   | argentine       | indian  |
| Transport     | train      | snowmobile     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-2::.
There 2 different types of food: cranberry, raspberry
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: techno, electronic
2 different pets are kept: hedgehog, turtle
The people use 2 different means of transport: subway, taxi
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
2. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Food          | raspberry | cranberry |
| Music-Genre   | techno       | electronic         |
| Pet           | turtle     | hedgehog         |
| Transport     | taxi    | subway    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, sudoku
The people have 2 different jobs:  freelancer, photographer
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, rock
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, motorbike
1. the fan of rock is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the freelancer##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |      2      |
| Hobby         | sudoku          | camping |
| Job           | photographer | freelancer     |
| Music-Genre   | disco            | rock         |
| Transport     | motorbike         | car   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: sprite, juice
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, horror
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, gospel
2 different pets are kept: frog, lizard
1. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3
2. the person drinking juice is the owner of the frog##1
3. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Beverage      | juice     | sprite   |
| Movie-Genre   | horror    | crime |
| Music-Genre   | punk   | gospel |
| Pet           | frog | lizard    |

