.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-20::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, soy-milk
There 2 different types of food: pomegranate, nectarine
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: indie, r&b
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, subway
1. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is the fan of indie##1
3. the fan of indie is the person driving the subway##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk     | tea |
| Food          | nectarine   | pomegranate |
| Music-Genre   | r&b     | indie     |
| Transport     | snowmobile | subway     |

 